name: ~ The Star Pharoah - Part I ~
description:
On the Night of the Grasping Moon, high priest Naneferkaptah awakes screaming. Between frantic gasps he utters his visions - an immense being supporting the sky, a face void of expression, with mystical limbs wielding the was-sceptre and royal regalia of office. It traverses time, and countless planes, to unite all under Cosmic Ttam. For when it comes, they will all be free of pain, and joy, and sorrow. Forever. They must prepare. There is little time.
